data.description: Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity in Tierrasanta! You'll Love this 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths in a highly desirable community, sitting on a corner lot. Its prime location places it near the freeway and just a stone's throw away from a thriving shopping center. Inside, you'll find a cozy fireplace and vaulted ceilings in the living room, creating a welcoming atmosphere. Additionally, there's one bedroom and a full bath on the lower level for added convenience.  The kitchen is flooded with natural light and leads to a spacious L-shaped patio, providing the perfect setting for your outdoor living needs. With private parking and plenty of it, parking is a breeze. New Windows throughout and front door can be moved to the side balcony location for a different entrance layout (HOA Approved). New tankless water heater and semi-new AC located in the backyard. This community offers an array of amenities, including a large lap pool, a kiddy pool, and a relaxing spa. Sports enthusiasts will appreciate the tennis courts and basketball court. For those who love outdoor activities, there's a picnic area and ample green spaces and walking paths for your daily exercise. This property won't last long, so be sure to schedule a viewing before it's too late. Your future home is waiting for you in this fantastic community. Make an appointment today!
